          <p class="card-desc">Multi-cashier point-of-sale system for a strawberry desserts shop. Product customizations, modifier support, and daily sales reports — designed for speed under real pressure.</p>
          <div class="chips">
            <span class="chip">React</span><span class="chip">JavaScript</span><span class="chip">Custom UI</span><span class="chip">Sales Reports</span>
          </div>
          <p class="insight">"Built from scratch. Real cashiers. Real customers. Real pressure."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
          <p class="card-tag">Enterprise · Zero-Error</p>
          <h3 class="card-title">VBA / SharePoint Automation Suite</h3>
          <p class="card-desc">Custom automation platform for industrial equipment procurement. Managed zero-error supply chains for Brose automotive (Querétaro) and Volkswagen (Silao) plants with long lead times on custom European equipment.</p>
          <div class="chips">
            <span class="chip">VBA</span><span class="chip">SharePoint</span><span class="chip">Google Cloud</span><span class="chip">Excel</span>
          </div>
          <p class="insight">"Long lead times on custom European equipment. Zero-error requirement. Delivered both."</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- ASIS — full width -->
      <div class="asis" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="asis-inner">
          <div>
            <p class="card-tag">AI · Personal · Trust</p>
            <h3 class="card-title" style="font-size:20px;">ASIS — Asistente MUY PERSONAL</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">A deeply personal AI assistant built to handle what matters most. Private, precise, and completely trusted. Not every system is built for a client — this one is the proof that the conviction goes beyond the professional.</p>
            <div class="chips" style="margin-top:16px;">
              <span class="chip">Claude API</span><span class="chip">Personal AI</span><span class="chip">Custom Architecture</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;">
            <div class="asis-quote">
              "You don't trust a technology with your most personal matters unless you truly believe in it. I built this for myself. That tells you everything about where I stand."
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="hint">Click any card to see the insight behind the build.</p>
    </div>
